high_descs: Go to the center kitchen console
Pick up the egg from the center kitchen console
Heat the egg in the microwave
Place the egg in the black bin
anns.task_desc: Place a heated egg in a bin

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the kitchen island.
Pick up the egg in front of the gold colored plate.
Walk around the kitchen island and to the stove on the right, look above the stove to face the microwave.
Place the egg inside the microwave, heat up the egg, take the egg out of the microwave.
Turn left, turn left at the fridge, turn left to face the kitchen island, and look down at the black bin.
Place the egg in the bin on the right side.
anns.task_desc: To heat an egg and place in the black bin.

high_descs: Turn right, to forward until two chairs are on right.  Turn right and proceed to counter and chairs.
Pick up egg from counter, in front of gold colored plate.
Turn around, proceed to sliding doors.  Turn left, proceed across room.  Turn left, proceed until stove is on right.  Turn to face stove.  Look up to microwave.
Open microwave door, put egg in microwave, close door.  Wait four seconds.  Open microwave door, remove egg, close microwave door.
Turn left, proceed until reach end of counter.  Turn left, then turn left to face counter and garbage can.
Place egg in right side of garbage can, to the right of the tomato and pump dispenser.
anns.task_desc: Move egg from counter, heat in microwave, put in garbage can.
